      Make Mother's Day truly special this year with a wonderful Brunch
      Buffet at either the Houston Center Club or the Plaza.  Center Club
      Chef Russell Knott and Plaza Chef Doug George are preparing an
      outstanding menu in honor of Mother's Day.

      And if you haven't found the perfect gift yet, consider a gift
      certificate from the Met's Bella Rinova Spa. Pamper her with a gift
      certificate of a facial, massage, pedicure or manicure at a Mother's
      Day Special Rate of 15% off all Mother's Day gift certificates.
      Contact Bella Rinova at 713-652-0700 to arrange your gift.



